{
  "stem": "15578.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I remember we went in the old country, everybody like a tailor, like me, had to go three years in the school at night time in order to finish as a, you know, if I want to open a shop, I have to finish a school.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After the school, you're going out, you could see Polish-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] young people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They'd stay with paint with brushes, going to brush your-- with paint up to-- that was very common.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In what year that was? 1938.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was always.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Always.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was always.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember it wasn't-- I was in bed still asleep, and all of a sudden, I heard something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, what's the matter?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't expect this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got up and said maybe it's raining or it start thunderstorm and that's all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then not very long they said it's a fire not very far where we used to live.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What is it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were two bombs right there that-- and a big-- what they did make materials, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and they bombed there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was the first bombs there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was about 5:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the name of that firm was Markowic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They made good materials.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bombed.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Markowic.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Air strike, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that time when it has started bomb, and the third day, everybody started to escape, to go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where are you going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the biggest mistake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on the way to Warsaw, that calls a small town, Rawa, that was a slaughter house at that time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the fourth day, say I'm going to Warsaw too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I took my bicycle and ride to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
